Java#

public class Potencias {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 10;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            System.out.println(n + "**" + i + ": " + (int) Math.pow(n, i));
        }
    }
}

C++#

#include <iostream>
#include <cmath>

int main() {
    int n = 10;
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        std::cout << n << "**" << i << ": " << static_cast<int>(pow(n, i)) << std::endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
